1
00:00:10,666 --> 00:00:15,069
<i>(Disonasu)</i>
<i>[triumphant laughter]</i>

2
00:00:15,103 --> 00:00:19,039
{\an1}Behold the Saesuri
that's slumbered
here so long!

3
00:00:19,072 --> 00:00:25,978
{\an4}A legacy of the past! It
wasn't easy obtaining it,
I didnt expect so much
resistance from the guards-

4
00:00:26,012 --> 00:00:29,749
{\an1}But at last! It's
all mine! [chuckle]

5
00:00:29,782 --> 00:00:30,817
{\an1}Then...

6
00:00:30,850 --> 00:00:32,751
[snicker]

7
00:00:32,784 --> 00:00:35,754
{\an5}<i>(Disonasu)</i>
<i>The head of your village</i>
<i>should habe minded his</i>
<i>own business!</i>

8
00:00:35,787 --> 00:00:39,657
{\an1}<i>I wasted precious time</i>
<i>gathering the sounds</i>
<i>he scattered about!</i>

9
00:00:43,860 --> 00:00:47,329
{\an1}So... the one who
attacked the village...!?

10
00:00:47,362 --> 00:00:51,300
{\an1}Was me. Or rather,
I put him up to it!

11
00:00:51,333 --> 00:00:55,303
Why you...!

12
00:00:55,336 --> 00:00:58,271
[grunt]

13
00:00:58,305 --> 00:01:00,941
[grunting]

14
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,681
[gasp]

15
00:01:10,515 --> 00:01:15,085
{\an4}You have absolutely no idea
what I've gone through in
order to try to regain the
power I lost!

16
00:01:15,118 --> 00:01:21,324
{\an4}After learning about the
legend of this place I went as
far as becoming the head of
Hachou Village to research it!

17
00:01:21,357 --> 00:01:24,260
And learn the
hidden secret...

18
00:01:24,293 --> 00:01:27,095
Now, where are the
remaining sounds?!

19
00:01:27,128 --> 00:01:29,831
I do not have
anymore time
to waste!

20
00:01:29,865 --> 00:01:33,234
Tell me, and you
can die without
pain...

21
00:01:33,267 --> 00:01:38,873
{\an5}...or I'll kill you
and make you talk with
the Reanimation Jutsu!
[evil laughter]

22
00:01:38,906 --> 00:01:40,406
You bastard!

23
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:45,744
[snear] Naruto...
You're really
quite amazing!

24
00:01:45,777 --> 00:01:49,046
I hear that you
brought down Pain
of the Akatsuki...

25
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:52,450
Even someone as
powerful as I was
couldn't defeat him!

26
00:01:52,483 --> 00:01:55,418
In fact, that's how
I lost my power...

27
00:01:55,452 --> 00:01:59,289
{\an1}I couldn't care
less about your
past!

28
00:01:59,322 --> 00:02:02,358
{\an1}If you lay a
hand on him...

29
00:02:02,391 --> 00:02:03,826
{\an1}I'll kill you!

30
00:02:03,859 --> 00:02:05,728
{\an1}[frightened gasp]

31
00:02:05,761 --> 00:02:08,763
[painful grunts]

32
00:02:08,796 --> 00:02:11,331
{\an1}Those snakes consume
chakra....

33
00:02:11,366 --> 00:02:17,738
{\an4}So the more that you
increase your chakra...
the tighter they'll
squeeze you...

34
00:02:20,273 --> 00:02:23,476
{\an1}[gasp] A snake!

35
00:02:23,509 --> 00:02:28,947
{\an4}You fool! You're so
full of yourself! Just
who do you think you
are, anyway!?

36
00:02:28,980 --> 00:02:31,048
{\an1}<i>You're nobody!</i>
<i>That's who!</i>

37
00:02:32,316 --> 00:02:36,219
{\an1}[frightened gasps]

38
00:02:36,252 --> 00:02:37,120
Hm.

39
00:02:39,455 --> 00:02:41,290
Here, just
take 'em!

40
00:02:41,323 --> 00:02:44,226
{\an5}Well, go on!
These are what
you want, aren't
they!?

41
00:02:45,192 --> 00:02:48,729
{\an1}Just take them and then
let Dokku Sensei and
Naruto go!

42
00:02:49,163 --> 00:02:52,332
{\an1}The kids have
the sounds!

43
00:02:52,365 --> 00:02:53,233
{\an1}[grunts]

44
00:02:53,266 --> 00:02:54,401
[gasp]

45
00:02:54,434 --> 00:02:57,437
{\an1}What!? They have them!?

46
00:02:57,470 --> 00:03:04,542
{\an1}They're above us. My
my, they're so brave.
They've come to save you.

47
00:03:04,576 --> 00:03:09,479
{\an1}It's Kabuto, or, more
likely a clone. And
five children.

48
00:03:09,513 --> 00:03:13,984
{\an1}It's the kids! I
wondered where they
went! Why!?

49
00:03:14,017 --> 00:03:16,887
{\an7}(Kakashi)
Then we'd better
approach cautiously.

50
00:05:05,442 --> 00:05:07,611
[gasps]
Sensei!

51
00:05:09,512 --> 00:05:11,014
Kids!!

52
00:05:15,918 --> 00:05:18,053
{\an1}[evil chuckle]

53
00:05:18,086 --> 00:05:22,322
{\an1}No, stop! Don't
you dare lay a
hand on them!

54
00:05:26,026 --> 00:05:28,162
{\an1}I have them all...

55
00:05:28,194 --> 00:05:32,197
{\an1}All seven of them...
I've done it! At last!

56
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:42,940
{\an1}Now I can finally get
my power back! Yes!
Yes!! [evil laughter]

57
00:05:42,973 --> 00:05:45,076
[struggling]

58
00:05:45,109 --> 00:05:47,077
<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>How do I get</i>
<i>out of this!?</i>

59
00:05:49,678 --> 00:05:52,081
<i>...consume chakra...</i>

60
00:05:56,451 --> 00:06:04,458
{\an4}<i>One gains control of the Ama no</i>
<i>Hoku's power by activating it</i>
<i>with a combination of seven</i>
<i>sounds input into the Saezuri.</i>

61
00:06:04,491 --> 00:06:12,198
{\an4}By Varying the patterns of
sounds entered into the Saezuri,
one can increase or decrease the
level of power available.

62
00:06:12,230 --> 00:06:18,368
{\an4}Already input sounds may be
manually updated, or it will
automatically update itself
every twelve hours.

63
00:06:18,402 --> 00:06:24,141
{\an4}If a sound pattern isn't
recognized, such as if it
doesn't exist in the Saezuri's
program...

64
00:06:24,174 --> 00:06:27,076
{\an1}...the previous pattern
will be maintained.

65
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:29,511
Now, if I did
this correctly...

66
00:06:34,415 --> 00:06:36,184
[satisfied sigh]

67
00:06:36,218 --> 00:06:39,653
[tones]

68
00:06:39,687 --> 00:06:43,190
[humming tones]

69
00:06:43,224 --> 00:06:45,457
[gasp]

70
00:06:45,491 --> 00:06:49,361
<i>(Mina)</i>
<i>[humming]</i>

71
00:06:53,232 --> 00:06:55,566
[loud explosion]

72
00:06:56,601 --> 00:06:58,002
[loud rumbling]

73
00:06:58,035 --> 00:06:59,536
{\an1}[falling back grunts]

74
00:06:59,569 --> 00:07:00,437
[gasp]

75
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:05,075
Mina!

76
00:07:13,715 --> 00:07:16,350
[struggling]

77
00:07:19,285 --> 00:07:21,287
{\an1}How could you
be so reckless!?

78
00:07:21,587 --> 00:07:23,422
'Cause...

79
00:07:23,456 --> 00:07:24,724
{\an1}We just wanted...

80
00:07:24,757 --> 00:07:27,093
To see you,
Sensei!!

81
00:07:27,126 --> 00:07:28,727
[gasp]

82
00:07:29,262 --> 00:07:34,331
[struggling]

83
00:07:48,210 --> 00:07:59,451
[loud rumbling]

84
00:07:59,485 --> 00:08:02,022
[laughter]

85
00:08:07,392 --> 00:08:11,229
{\an1}Amazing... amazing!
Amazing! [laughter]

86
00:08:11,262 --> 00:08:13,064
{\an1}Quite impressive...

87
00:08:13,764 --> 00:08:17,466
The Ama...
no  Hoku!

88
00:08:19,236 --> 00:08:25,407
{\an1}With this activation
pattern... the way
to release power!

89
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:27,108
{\an1}<i>(Kakashi)</i>
<i>Too much ambition...</i>

90
00:08:27,142 --> 00:08:28,576
[angry grunt]

91
00:08:28,609 --> 00:08:33,280
{\an4}...will destroy you.
This isn't something
anyone should use
anymore.

92
00:08:35,648 --> 00:08:38,785
{\an1}<i>I looked you up in an</i>
<i>old wanted criminals</i>
<i>report...</i>

93
00:08:38,818 --> 00:08:42,788
{\an1}<i>...it was believed you </i>
<i>died in a scuffle with</i>
<i>the Akatsuki.</i>

94
00:08:42,821 --> 00:08:45,824
{\an1}<i>...You specialized</i>
<i>in Summoning Jutsu...</i>

95
00:08:45,858 --> 00:08:50,261
{\an4}<i>...You were known </i>
<i>as a homicidal maniac</i>
<i>who claimed thousands</i>
<i>of victims...</i>

96
00:08:50,294 --> 00:08:55,298
{\an4}<i>...and together with</i>
<i>Orochimaru, you </i>
<i>researched the forbiddin</i>
<i>Reanimation Jutsu.</i>

97
00:08:55,333 --> 00:08:57,433
[evil chuckle]

98
00:08:57,466 --> 00:09:00,703
{\an1}Surrender, Disonasu.

99
00:09:03,638 --> 00:09:04,806
{\an3}[gasp]

100
00:09:09,643 --> 00:09:11,678
{\an1}[large explosion]

101
00:09:11,712 --> 00:09:12,579
[gasp]

102
00:09:26,291 --> 00:09:27,625
[gasp]

103
00:09:31,161 --> 00:09:43,738
[growling]

104
00:09:43,771 --> 00:09:50,211
[loud roar]

105
00:09:53,813 --> 00:10:03,821
{\an1}<i>(Nine Tails Clone)</i>
<i>[snarling]</i>

106
00:10:03,855 --> 00:10:12,795
{\an1}<i>(Nine Tails Clone)</i>
<i>[snarling]</i>

107
00:10:12,828 --> 00:10:14,364
Brother..!

108
00:10:14,398 --> 00:10:16,098
{\an1}Shiseru!

109
00:10:17,233 --> 00:10:18,867
[gasp]

110
00:10:24,638 --> 00:10:26,408
You're mine!!

111
00:10:30,743 --> 00:10:32,413
{\an1}[snicker]

112
00:10:32,445 --> 00:10:34,579
{\an1}(Nine Tails Clone)
[growling]

113
00:10:34,613 --> 00:10:35,747
[gasps]

114
00:10:38,450 --> 00:10:41,619
[roaring]

115
00:10:41,652 --> 00:10:44,755
{\an1}<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Hey! Leave that</i>
<i>one to me!</i>

116
00:10:48,925 --> 00:10:50,694
Naruto?

117
00:10:50,727 --> 00:10:51,760
Naruto!

118
00:10:51,795 --> 00:10:53,529
Naruto!

119
00:11:01,336 --> 00:11:10,444
[roaring]

120
00:11:11,744 --> 00:11:14,180
[explosion]

121
00:11:14,213 --> 00:11:18,216
[coughing]

122
00:11:18,249 --> 00:11:20,617
{\an1}[fighting grunts]

123
00:11:23,455 --> 00:11:24,621
[evil chuckle]

124
00:11:36,298 --> 00:11:38,266
[grunts]

125
00:11:41,469 --> 00:11:42,803
[gasp]

126
00:11:45,772 --> 00:11:47,374
Hmph!

127
00:11:47,807 --> 00:11:55,214
{\an4}[slurp]
[evil laugh]
It's all over for
you guys now!

128
00:11:58,816 --> 00:12:01,386
{\an1}[gasp] Ino!
Choji!

129
00:12:03,854 --> 00:12:05,521
{\an3}[gasp]

130
00:12:05,554 --> 00:12:07,790
{\an1}[fighting grunts]

131
00:12:08,758 --> 00:12:10,459
Sakura!

132
00:12:10,893 --> 00:12:13,396
{\an1}Now here's a little
taste of my genius!

133
00:12:20,502 --> 00:12:25,205
{\an1}You'll soon see that
art, is an explosion!

134
00:12:29,008 --> 00:12:32,377
{\an1}He needs to create
a curse mark in order
to perform the ritual.

135
00:12:32,411 --> 00:12:35,280
{\an1}So we can't give
him a chance to
do that!

136
00:12:36,348 --> 00:12:38,482
{\an1}No way!

137
00:12:42,752 --> 00:12:45,621
[roaring]

138
00:13:00,435 --> 00:13:02,768
{\an1}[injured screech]

139
00:13:09,874 --> 00:13:14,778
{\an1}[screaming in pain]

140
00:13:16,013 --> 00:13:22,952
{\an1}<i>(Nine Tails Clone)</i>
<i>[exhausted panting]</i>

141
00:13:22,985 --> 00:13:27,722
How can you...!?
What are you!?

142
00:13:27,756 --> 00:13:33,295
The power you possess,
how did you ever get
so much power?!

143
00:13:33,328 --> 00:13:40,300
{\an4}Over the years up 'til now,
there have been many people
who've taught me a whole lot
of really important lessons.

144
00:13:40,333 --> 00:13:47,372
{\an1}<i>Even right now in the present,</i>
<i>I've learned something from an</i>
<i>incredibly strong person...</i>

145
00:13:47,406 --> 00:13:55,313
{\an4}My strength, my power...
isn't just the Rasengan or
Sage Jutsu, or even the Nine
Tails chakra...

146
00:13:55,346 --> 00:13:58,782
{\an1}No, my true power...

147
00:14:05,387 --> 00:14:07,456
{\an1}Is right here!

148
00:14:07,490 --> 00:14:10,657
[roaring]

149
00:14:16,729 --> 00:14:17,998
Sai...!

150
00:14:18,031 --> 00:14:19,866
{\an1}[sheepish chuckle]

151
00:14:27,772 --> 00:14:31,909
{\an1}Reanimated Shinobi that
don't regenerate?

152
00:14:31,942 --> 00:14:35,579
{\an1}I guess... they were
sacrificial pawns.

153
00:14:35,613 --> 00:14:37,981
[struggling]

154
00:14:38,014 --> 00:14:40,782
{\an1}[chuckle] Looks like
we finally got you.

155
00:14:40,816 --> 00:14:43,952
{\an1}I'll get you!

156
00:14:43,986 --> 00:14:47,623
Your ability is
useless without backup
to support you!

157
00:14:47,655 --> 00:14:50,758
{\an1}It requires too many
steps to complete!

158
00:14:50,791 --> 00:14:54,495
{\an1}Backup, huh? Well...

159
00:14:54,529 --> 00:14:55,996
Hm.

160
00:14:58,898 --> 00:15:01,867
{\an1}Damn! That guy is
such a nuisance!

161
00:15:05,770 --> 00:15:08,606
Now then...

162
00:15:10,073 --> 00:15:13,709
[painful grunts]

163
00:15:13,743 --> 00:15:15,078
[struggling]

164
00:15:15,112 --> 00:15:18,481
{\an1}I won't let you
go any further!

165
00:15:18,514 --> 00:15:20,550
Not a chance!

166
00:15:20,583 --> 00:15:22,017
I won't stop!

167
00:15:22,050 --> 00:15:23,218
Give it up!

168
00:15:23,251 --> 00:15:29,557
No! Never! I won't
give up! Not when
I'm this close!

169
00:15:30,690 --> 00:15:36,695
[tones]

170
00:15:37,197 --> 00:15:40,365
[running]

171
00:15:42,867 --> 00:15:48,705
<i>(Mina)</i>
<i>[humming]</i>

172
00:15:48,738 --> 00:15:49,973
[gasp]

173
00:15:51,007 --> 00:15:58,480
{\an1}[rumbling]

174
00:15:58,514 --> 00:16:01,015
{\an1}[frightened gasps]

175
00:17:12,808 --> 00:17:13,709
[gasp]

176
00:17:15,177 --> 00:17:16,479
[surprised gasp]

177
00:17:17,713 --> 00:17:20,948
[explosion]

178
00:17:26,919 --> 00:17:28,555
{\an1}Argh!

179
00:17:36,161 --> 00:17:39,765
Ah, is this--?
Huh!?

180
00:17:48,804 --> 00:17:51,073
Hey, stop!

181
00:17:51,106 --> 00:17:54,842
What the hell!?
Damn you!!!

182
00:18:12,957 --> 00:18:16,894
[grunts]

183
00:18:16,927 --> 00:18:22,232
[panting]

184
00:18:22,266 --> 00:18:28,538
{\an4}Well, seems those clone
snakes that constitute
your body have a very
big defect.

185
00:18:28,571 --> 00:18:42,315
[dying grunts]

186
00:18:42,349 --> 00:18:47,886
{\an4}They mature quickly, but
reach the end of their
lifespan just as fast, and
then, that's that.

187
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:52,224
{\an1}Of course, just in
case, I came up with
20 other strategies.

188
00:18:52,257 --> 00:18:54,760
{\an1}...but I'm glad they
weren't neccessary.

189
00:19:02,065 --> 00:19:03,899
{\an1}[thunder and lightning]

190
00:19:03,933 --> 00:19:05,868
{\an1}[screams]

191
00:19:10,105 --> 00:19:12,540
{\an1}Woah, what
was that!?

192
00:19:13,274 --> 00:19:15,577
{\an1}Look...

193
00:19:18,812 --> 00:19:20,848
{\an1}The ground just
caved in!

194
00:19:22,115 --> 00:19:26,952
{\an4}This entire area must
have been elevated and
supported by those
tree roots...!

195
00:19:26,985 --> 00:19:30,021
We have to get
away from the
hole... fast!

196
00:19:30,055 --> 00:19:31,156
{\an1}Yeah.

197
00:19:32,224 --> 00:19:35,593
Sensei? Is that
giant thing ever
going to stop?

198
00:19:39,830 --> 00:19:48,737
{\an1}[thunder and lightning]

199
00:19:48,771 --> 00:19:50,706
{\an1}[explosion]

200
00:19:50,739 --> 00:20:01,280
{\an1}[thunder and lightning]

201
00:20:12,891 --> 00:20:19,262
The unleashed power
will cloak the world
...and destroy it.

202
00:20:30,971 --> 00:20:36,644
Power... if I can
just bathe in all
that power...

203
00:20:36,677 --> 00:20:37,377
{\an3}[gasp]

204
00:20:43,415 --> 00:20:45,284
[frightened breaths]

205
00:20:53,390 --> 00:20:54,792
{\an3}[gasp]

206
00:21:16,743 --> 00:21:21,948
[roaring]

207
00:22:55,457 --> 00:22:59,127
{\an4}<i>(Dokku)</i>
<i>That's why I will</i>
<i>never let go of</i>
<i>you again!</i>

208
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:02,330
{\an4}<i>(Dokku)</i>
<i>If you do fall, </i>
<i>then we'll fall</i>
<i>together!</i>

209
00:23:02,363 --> 00:23:05,065
<i>(Shiseru)</i>
<i>I've been in love with</i>
<i>you, too! Since then!</i>

210
00:23:05,098 --> 00:23:09,369
<i>(Shiseru)</i>
<i>But Dokku, who's going</i>
<i>to protect the children!?</i>

211
00:23:09,403 --> 00:23:12,872
{\an5}<i>(Shiseru)</i>
<i>You're the only one who</i>
<i>can save them! And save</i>
<i>their future too!</i>

212
00:23:12,905 --> 00:23:14,807
{\an1}<i>(Dokku)</i>
<i>But... but I--!</i>

213
00:23:14,840 --> 00:23:19,778
{\an7}<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Next time, on Naruto</i>
<i>Shippuden: "Power-</i>
<i>Episode Final." </i>

214
00:23:22,346 --> 00:23:24,114
{\an1}Please save them.

